{"tid":2363663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國多間企業警告 : 若共和黨議員挑戰拜登當選，將會停止捐獻 !","createTime":"2021-01-12T11:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T12:12:17.000Z","uid":219007,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3435b154fc0c092e0c977a290d36548ffde13933","tid":2363663,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:21:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570024-20210112.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570024-20210112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJufUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=5fda33f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570024-20210112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=34b8845e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570024-20210112.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國十多間主要企業警告，若國會共和黨議員在任何表決中，投票支持挑戰拜登當選總統的結果，將會停止捐獻。<br />\n<br />\n參與行動的大企業，包括萬豪酒店集團、花旗銀行，以及谷歌等主要科企；有其他公司就在國會遭衝擊事件後，考慮調整捐獻策略。<br />\n<br />\n德勤會計師事務所、AT&amp;T、美國運通卡及萬事達卡公司都表示，會暫時停止捐獻款項。Airbnb就說會繼續秉持公司的社區政策，當確認某人與暴力或仇恨組織為伍，將採取禁制措施。"},{"pid":"ca2fe523179fa8ba9e705922f9b2a914970d3ab2","tid":2363663,"uid":10637,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:23:07.000Z","msg":"連燈仔準備罷用citi visa同master card<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3faad6dc77b422c7ee6d188976e7e211e92c993b","tid":2363663,"uid":49853,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"唔俾反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15223bcb8bcb3f2c2b843a4f43f7f57bd4ea55b6","tid":2363663,"uid":144541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score